## ZkSync driver
#ZKSYNC_RINKEBY_RPC_ADDRESS=https://rinkeby-api.zksync.io/jsrpc
#ZKSYNC_MAINNET_RPC_ADDRESS=https://api.zksync.io/jsrpc
